 – howe cardin howe acting michaud chevrier marler hees balcer mcilraith pickersgill hellyer richardson acting jamieson marchand lang mazankowski pépin axworthy mazankowski crosbie bouchard lewis corbeil young anderson collenette valeri lapierre ministers of transport infrastructure and communities – cannon baird strahl lebel raitt ministers of transport –present garneau v t e ministers of foreign affairs secretaries of state for external affairs – murphy roche borden meighen king meighen king bennett king st laurent pearson diefenbaker smith diefenbaker acting green martin sharp maceachen jamieson macdonald macguigan ministers of external affairs – maceachen chrétien clark mcdougall beatty ouellet ministers of foreign affairs – ouellet axworthy manley graham pettigrew mackay bernier emerson cannon baird fast acting nicholson dion freeland retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlejohnbairdcanadianpoliticianoldid categories  birthscanadian ministers of the environmentcanadian ministers of foreign affairscanadian ministers of transportconservative party of canada mpsliving peoplemembers of the th canadian ministrymembers of the executive council of ontariomembers of the house of commons of canada from ontariomembers of the queens privy council for canadaqueens university alumnipoliticians from ottawaprogressive conservative party of ontario mppsbarrick goldcanadian pacific railway peoplehidden categories webarchive template wayback linkswikipedia pending changes protected pages level good articlesuse mdy dates from september pages using infobox officeholder with an atypical party valueblp articles lacking sources from september all blp articles lacking sourcesall articles with vague or ambiguous timevague or ambiguous time from january all articles with unsourced statementsarticles with unsourced statements from september all articles with specifically marked weaselworded phrasesarticles with specifically marked weaselworded phrases from march  navigation menu 